,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cf97919fa2800fb85d9d9833f2b33660107b003","tid":656134,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"若果2數hcf為a 相差亦能被a整除"},{"pid":"6d2796825e6a19e69615600057afdf4ab9f8cafc","tid":656134,"uid":34189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/134718_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F134718_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=4353f6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁,雖然畫得衰,但當每格都同樣大小啦<br />\n一格=GCD<br />\n咁2個數好自然比GCD除得盡<br />\n然後大嘅數如果除細嘅數<br />\n得出嘅remainder同樣可以比GCD整除<br />\n將個remainder取代x嘅數值,如果我哋用新數值嘅黎揾嘅GCD<br />\n其實個GCD係冇變過<br />\n咁我哋就可以不斷重覆呢個動作<br />\n最後就會得到果格GCD嘅數值"},{"pid":"d40b1aa6528559f60440bd0bdf7c887ea3aa9224","tid":656134,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1633acc94f08a34e9190036c6118774ba15007d9","tid":656134,"uid":51129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"1)若q整除a,b，則q整除a,b-ax；反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n2)換言之尋找(a,b)嘅公因數相當於尋找(a,b-ax)嘅公因數<br />\n<br />\n3)Euclidean Algorithm就係反覆運用(a,b) -&gt; (a,b-ax)將兩個數字變細，令問題簡化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"點解只要q可整除b,就可以整除b-ax"},{"pid":"4e447ec4785e3181ac709b6a3c3ef0d22dd34e77","tid":656134,"uid":166291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40b1aa6528559f60440bd0bdf7c887ea3aa9224","tid":656134,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1633acc94f08a34e9190036c6118774ba15007d9","tid":656134,"uid":51129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"1)若q整除a,b，則q整除a,b-ax；反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n2)換言之尋找(a,b)嘅公因數相當於尋找(a,b-ax)嘅公因數<br />\n<br />\n3)Euclidean Algorithm就係反覆運用(a,b) -&gt; (a,b-ax)將兩個數字變細，令問題簡化"},"